Build a modern full-stack productivity dashboard called TeamPulse.

Tech stack:
- Next.js 15
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- shadcn/ui
- Recharts
- Lucide Icons

Requirements:

Create a modern SaaS-style dashboard with:

1. Dashboard page
- KPI cards
- Team productivity chart
- Tasks completed chart
- Recent activity feed

2. Task Management page
- Kanban board
- Todo / In Progress / Done columns
- Drag and drop support
- Mock data

3. Team page
- Team member cards
- Avatar
- Role
- Productivity score

4. Settings page
- Dark mode toggle
- Notification preferences
- User profile section

Design requirements:
- Modern SaaS look
- Beautiful gradients
- Responsive layout
- Sidebar navigation
- Clean typography
- Smooth animations

Generate:
- Complete project structure
- Reusable components
- Mock data
- README.md
- Well-organized folders

The application should be fully functional using mock data and look production-ready.
